HEADWORD: Disrespect
<hw>Dis`re*spect"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Want of respect
or reverence; disesteem; incivility; discourtesy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Impatience of bearing the least affront or
<qex>disrespect</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

